name: Savior of the Magislayers - Jeanne D'arc
effect:
3 Level 8 "Magislayer" Monsters
This card can only be Xyz Summoned OR Special Summoned by an "Magislay" or "Magikill" card effect, and can't be Summoned by other ways. You can only Special Summon 1 "Magislayer Guardian - Jeanne D'arc" per turn. You can Special Summon this card from your Extra Deck by sending 3 Spell/Traps you control to the GY. Once while this card is face-up on the Field, If this card was Summoned on this turn and has no Materials (Quick Effect): You can attach up to 3 Spell/Traps from your GY to this card as Xyz Materials, this effect cannot be negated. Once per turn, you can detach 1 Xyz Material from this card: Special Summon 1 "Magislayer" Monster from your GY or Banish Zone to your Field, regardless of that Send 1 "Magislay" or "Magikill" card from your hand or Deck to your GY. (Quick Effect): You can banish this card you control, and if you do, Special Summon 1 non-Xyz "Magislayer" Monster that is banished. You can only activate this effect of "Savior of the Magislayers - Jeanne D'arc" once per turn.
